## Quick Start ğŸƒâ€â™‚ï¸

### Local Development

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/newcl/mytube.git
cd mytube

# Start with Docker Compose
docker-compose up -d
```

### Kubernetes Deployment

```bash
# Deploy to your cluster
helm install mytube ./k8s/mytube
```

